These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, water, 7up
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, poker, canasta
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | 7up | water | soy-milk | mirinda   |
| Game   | scrabble  | bridge     | poker   | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, iris, daffodil
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, satire, western, disaster
1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | iris | daffodil | dahlia | zinnia    |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | satire      | scientific | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, red, blood-red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, climbing, sailing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who likes ebony is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color         | ebony | blood-red | red   | apricot |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | climbing | sailing | snowboarding         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, woodworking, photography
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, january, may
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | photography | gardening | magic-tricks  | woodworking      |
| Birthday         | february | may   | january | september |

