.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, fishing, baking
City: colone, paris, marseilles, berlin
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby   | baking | fishing | rock-climbing | gardening |
| City    | colone       | berlin | marseilles | paris     |

