.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, horror, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, van, motorbike, tram
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | horror | animation | mystery |
| Transport           | car      | motorbike | tram | van    |

