.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster, oliveros, aristoff
City: marseilles, miami, paris, hannover
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Cigar   | oliveros | bluemaster | cain | aristoff  |
| City           | paris | marseilles | hannover       | miami |

