2. the person who's sport is climbing is the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | metal | jazz      | pop | punk |
| Sport   | rowing          | tennis | golf     | climbing    |

