2. the fisherman is on the left of the german##1
3. the software-developer is on the far right##1
4. the british is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the russian is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Job   | lawyer    | dancer       | fisherman | software-developer   |
| Nationality     | british | japanese | russian   | german |

