2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Sport      | swimming | snowboarding  | lacrosse | rugby |
| Flower   | amaryllis  | daffodil | balloon-flower           | rose   |

