3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating mango##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | mango | orange | peas | grapes  |
| City           | san-francisco | london      | hannover | new-york |

