2. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| House   | palace | farmhouse     | colonial | townhouse |
| Food         | asparagus | cabbage | cherry   | tomato   |

