.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, turtle, dog
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia, aquamarine, white
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the dog is the person who likes white##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Pet   | lizard | turtle | frog | dog   |
| Color     | aquamarine  | pink    | fuchsia       | white |

 